OL,3,CRicky Hatton charity 'will help as
OL,4,Cmany people as possible'
OL,6,FThe son of the late boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,7,Fhas revealed plans for a new mental
OL,8,Fhealth charity in his dad's name so
OL,9,F"no one ever has to face those battles
OL,10,Falone."
OL,12,FThe Ricky Hatton Foundation will be
OL,13,Fset up to carry on the former boxing
OL,14,Fworld champion's spirit and "help as
OL,15,Fmany people as possible", Campbell
OL,16,FHatton said in a post on Instagram.
