OL,3,CRicky Hatton charity 'will help as
OL,4,Cmany people as possible'
OL,6,FThe charity said: "While it's been a
OL,7,Fdifficult time for everyone, we are
OL,8,Fdetermined that the foundation will
OL,9,Fcarry on Ricky's spirit to help as
OL,10,Fmany people as possible in their fight
OL,11,Fagainst mental illness."
OL,13,FThe boxing icon was found dead at the
OL,14,Fage of 46 on 14 September. Although
OL,15,Fthere has been no inquest into his
OL,16,Fdeath yet, police, who found his body
OL,17,Fat his Hyde home, say they are not
OL,18,Ftreating his death as suspicious.
