OL,3,CRicky Hatton charity 'will help as
OL,4,Cmany people as possible'
OL,6,FThe sporting icon, who was a father-of-
OL,7,Fthree and grandfather, was often open
OL,8,Fabout his own struggles with mental
OL,9,Fhealth and urged others to speak up.
OL,11,FHis loved ones hope the new foundation
OL,12,Fwill be a "powerful vehicle to bring
OL,13,Fpeople together, spark conversation
OL,14,Fand drive positive change."
OL,16,FThe charity says sport will "be at the
OL,17,Fheart" of its work and its mission
OL,18,Fwill be to raise awareness of mental
OL,19,Fhealth, remove the stigma, and offer
OL,20,Fdirect support through talking
OL,21,Ftherapies and community programmes.
