OL,6,FThe former world champion's funeral
OL,7,Fwill take place at Manchester
OL,8,FCathedral on Friday, 10 October.
OL,10,FFans will have a chance to pay their
OL,11,Frespects to the boxer as his cortege
OL,12,Fdrives past a number of personal
OL,13,Flandmarks around his hometown of Hyde,
OL,14,Fbefore continuing into Manchester and
OL,15,Fending at the Etihad Stadium.
OL,17,FIn an exclusive interview with ITV
OL,18,FGranada Reports, Campbell Hatton said
OL,19,Fhis dad would "want the streets to be
OL,20,Ffull of people...because everything he
OL,21,Fdid, he did for his fans."
